graph TB
    subgraph "KServe Control Plane"
        Controller[KServe Controller Manager<br/>Go Operator]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>:9443 HTTPS TLS 1.2+]
        Controller -->|validates/mutates| Webhook
    end

    subgraph "Model Serving Components"
        StorageInit[Storage Initializer<br/>Python Init Container]
        Agent[KServe Agent<br/>Go Sidecar]
        Router[KServe Router<br/>InferenceGraph Routing]
        LocalModel[LocalModel Manager<br/>Go Service]
        LocalAgent[LocalModelNode Agent<br/>Go DaemonSet]
    end

    subgraph "Model Servers"
        HF[HuggingFace Server<br/>Python - Transformers/LLMs]
        SKLearn[Sklearn Server<br/>Python - Scikit-learn]
        XGB[XGBoost Server<br/>Python - XGBoost]
        LGB[LightGBM Server<br/>Python - LightGBM]
        Paddle[Paddle Server<br/>Python - PaddlePaddle]
        PMML[PMML Server<br/>Python - PMML]
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        InferenceService[InferenceService CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1beta1]
        ServingRuntime[ServingRuntime CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        ClusterServingRuntime[ClusterServingRuntime CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        InferenceGraph[InferenceGraph CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        LLMInferenceService[LLMInferenceService CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        TrainedModel[TrainedModel CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
    end

    User[User/CI] -->|creates| InferenceService
    User -->|creates| LLMInferenceService
    User -->|creates| InferenceGraph

    InferenceService -->|watched by| Controller
    LLMInferenceService -->|watched by| Controller
    InferenceGraph -->|watched by| Controller
    ServingRuntime -->|watched by| Controller
    ClusterServingRuntime -->|watched by| Controller
    TrainedModel -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|creates| KnativeService[Knative Service<br/>Serverless Mode]
    Controller -->|creates| Deployment[Kubernetes Deployment<br/>Raw Mode]
    Controller -->|creates| VirtualService[Istio VirtualService<br/>Traffic Routing]
    Controller -->|creates| DestinationRule[Istio DestinationRule<br/>Load Balancing]

    StorageInit -->|downloads from| S3[S3/GCS/Azure Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    StorageInit -->|downloads from| HFHub[HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]

    Deployment -->|contains| StorageInit
    Deployment -->|contains| Agent
    Deployment -->|contains| HF
    Deployment -->|contains| SKLearn

    InferenceGraph -->|uses| Router
    Router -->|routes to| HF
    Router -->|routes to| SKLearn

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        Istio[Istio 1.17+<br/>Service Mesh]
        Knative[Knative Serving 1.8+<br/>Serverless Platform]
        CertManager[cert-manager 1.0+<br/>Certificate Management]
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API 1.25+<br/>Orchestration]
    end

    Controller -->|depends on| Istio
    Controller -->|depends on| Knative
    Controller -->|depends on| CertManager
    Controller -->|integrates| K8sAPI

    subgraph "Internal ODH/RHOAI"
        ServiceMesh[Service Mesh<br/>mTLS Enforcement]
        Authorino[Authorino<br/>Token Authorization]
        ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>Metadata/Versioning]
        DSPipelines[Data Science Pipelines<br/>ML Pipeline Integration]
    end

    Controller -->|integrates| ServiceMesh
    Controller -->|integrates| Authorino
    Controller -->|integrates| ModelRegistry
    DSPipelines -->|deploys via| InferenceService

    LocalModel -->|manages| LocalAgent
    LocalAgent -->|runs on| WorkerNode[Worker Nodes<br/>GPU/CPU Resources]

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:3px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style InferenceService fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style LLMInferenceService fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style InferenceGraph fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Istio fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Knative fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style CertManager fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style K8sAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style ServiceMesh fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Authorino fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style ModelRegistry fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style DSPipelines fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style S3 fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style HFHub fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
